com.pogofish.jadt.parser
Interface ParserImpl

All Known Implementing Classes:
JavaCCParserImpl
public interface ParserImpl

Interface for internal parser implementations used by the StandardParser The idea is that StandardParser provides a stateless facaade to the world while ParseImpl may be stateful

Author:
jiry
